      "rationale": "In-vitro hemolysis experiments conducted at all five COU operating points (flow rates 2–6 L/min, rotational speeds 2 000–3 500 rpm) in a closed-loop mock circulatory loop. Measured flow rates within ±1.4 % and speeds within ±0.8 % of nominal. Temperature controlled to 37 ± 0.5 °C throughout."
    },
