      "rationale": "Three-layer MLP surrogate approximates the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model integrated along CFD-computed streamlines. Architecture selection based on hyperparameter search over depth (2–5 layers) and width (64–256 units); 3×128 configuration minimised validation loss. Model form documented in surrogate development report SR-2024-07."
